<span id="iv.7.xiii-p21"></span>11. The day for building thy walls!  
That day! Removed far shall be the decree:

<span id="iv.7.xiii-p22"></span>*12. That day! Even to thee shall they
come,  
From Assyria and cities of fortress,  
And from the fortress even to the river,  
And* from *sea to sea, and* from *mountain to mountain,  
